cats.name: Fluffy
cats.description: Fluffy is a playful and affectionate Persian cat. She loves to cuddle and is great with kids and other pets. She has been spayed and is up to date on all of her vaccinations.

cats.name: Simba
cats.description: Simba is a handsome and friendly Siamese cat. He loves to play and is very curious about his surroundings. He has been neutered and is up to date on all of his vaccinations.

cats.name: Luna

cats.name: Oreo
cats.description: Oreo is a gentle and laid-back Maine Coon cat. He loves to be petted and is great with children. He has been neutered and is up to date on all of his vaccinations.

cats.name: Smokey

cats.name: Mittens

cats.name: Whiskers

cats.name: Milo
